{"tid":1938161,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[小任務] 請問有冇手足反對出酒牌?","createTime":"2020-03-22T10:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T13:22:40.000Z","uid":193239,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"07710d196bc650915324bf0c158448ffcba96cc4","tid":1938161,"uid":193239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T10:57:41.000Z","msg":"酒牌局周二舉行會議<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n下稿代酒牌局發出：<br />\n <br />\n　　酒牌局星期二（三月二十四日）舉行會議，討論五宗酒牌新申請、續期及轉讓個案。<br />\n　　 <br />\n　　有關申請如下（不依照討論次序）：<br />\n <br />\n香港：<br />\n───<br />\n位於上環的LAMBDA LOUNGE<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">位於黃竹坑的香港警察學院警官會所</span><br />\n <br />\n九龍：<br />\n───<br />\n位於旺角的迷城及The Oak<br />\n <br />\n新界：<br />\n───<br />\n位於長洲的彗星廊卡拉OK<br />\n <br />\n　　酒牌局會議於上午九時四十五分在灣仔皇后大道東258號一樓102號會議室舉行。為應對2019冠狀病毒病疫情，避免人群於密閉空間聚集，以保障所有人士的健康，現階段所有酒牌局公開聆訊暫不設公眾席。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年3月22日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間11時00分"},{"pid":"91ab7c8ff23a0b3867cdaf8adbf36e7fbf3d7dc0","tid":1938161,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T10:59:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a43c1d195b5739dd665b633da4b20dc10ad396cc","tid":1938161,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T10:59:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"958788c577763bb601204ab29461592cf9a55fa0","tid":1938161,"uid":193239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T10:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a2d2e13719b674065b961c6a042e00f8ffc2a9","tid":1938161,"uid":193239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T11:00:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c726a945a0d1a49dce89908901a74355e0d80d0","tid":1938161,"uid":193239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202